{
  "id": "adv_event_2408_01_05_01",
  "title": "偽りのREALISM ～密着 新曲会議！？～ 5話 敵はやっぱり",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――密着取材、最終日",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "スリクスのセンターは私よ",
      "startTime": 2.2000001192,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kor001.wav",
      "text": "真ん中に立つのは当然でしょ",
      "startTime": 4.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そんなの、ただの思考停止じゃん",
      "startTime": 7.3666667859,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kan001.wav",
      "text": "曲を大事にしない人は、センターに相応しくないでーす",
      "startTime": 11,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……え？　franとkanaが喧嘩しているのに",
      "startTime": 15.9666667859,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-mhk001.wav",
      "text": "そんなに平然としていていいのかって？",
      "startTime": 19.3469964181,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私達は固い絆で結ばれていると信じていますが",
      "startTime": 22.5000001192,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-mhk002.wav",
      "text": "なあなあの馴れ合いがいいとも思っていません",
      "startTime": 26.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "お互い、忌憚のない意見をぶつけ合いますし――",
      "startTime": 29.3000001192,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-mhk003.wav",
      "text": "時にはあんな風に、喧嘩になることだってありますよ",
      "startTime": 33,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-mhk004.wav",
      "text": "……本当に、たまにですけどね",
      "startTime": 36.5333334525,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "二人とも、そのくらいにしておきなさい",
      "startTime": 39.4000001192,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-mhk005.wav",
      "text": "今回は……そうね、私もkanaと同意見よ",
      "startTime": 43.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ただ、今までの私達のイメージを崩したくないから……",
      "startTime": 48.7666667859,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-mhk006.wav",
      "text": "そうね、2コーラス目ではfranがこっちに……",
      "startTime": 53.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "（な、なんとか誤魔化せた……か？）",
      "startTime": 58.2333334525,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-koh001.wav",
      "text": "（良かった、どうなることかと思った……！！）",
      "startTime": 62.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あー、やっと密着取材終わったー！！",
      "startTime": 67.7666667859,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kan002.wav",
      "text": "これでカメラに追いかけられないで済むー！！",
      "startTime": 72.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-mhk007.wav",
      "text": "本当にね",
      "startTime": 75.8000001192,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "それにしてもさあ、あんた達、見てた？",
      "startTime": 77.3666667859,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kan003.wav",
      "text": "最後に喧嘩してた時の{user}の顔！",
      "startTime": 81.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "こりゃ事務所クビになるな、再就職どうしようって",
      "startTime": 86.1333334525,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kan004.wav",
      "text": "絶望ぶりだったわ",
      "startTime": 90.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "さすがにそこまでは考えてませんでしたけど……",
      "startTime": 92.6000001192,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-koh002.wav",
      "text": "でも本当に肝が冷えたんですからね！？",
      "startTime": 96.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kor002.wav",
      "text": "ぷぷ……",
      "startTime": 99.2666667859,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-mhk008.wav",
      "text": "……ふ、くくっ",
      "startTime": 100.5999940157,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kan005.wav",
      "text": "……あはは、あははははは！！",
      "startTime": 102.2999970674,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "だって順調に仕事して仕事して曲作って終了、じゃ",
      "startTime": 105.8666637341,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kor003.wav",
      "text": "番組として面白くないじゃないですか",
      "startTime": 111.5333302815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "だからkana達が、番組の盛り上げどころを",
      "startTime": 114.6999970674,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kan006.wav",
      "text": "作ってあげたって訳",
      "startTime": 117.7333302815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私のドッキリにGO出したのはまだ恨んでますけど",
      "startTime": 119.9333304007,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kor004.wav",
      "text": "仕掛け人をやりたい気持ちは、ちょーっと分かりました",
      "startTime": 123.7333302815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "確かに……みなさんが喧嘩するのはいつも通りですけど",
      "startTime": 127.8333304007,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-koh003.wav",
      "text": "喧嘩の内容は、いつもより真剣だったような……？",
      "startTime": 132.3666636149,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "それでは、私達がいつも馬鹿馬鹿しいことでしか",
      "startTime": 136.9333304007,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-mhk009.wav",
      "text": "喧嘩していないみたいじゃないですか",
      "startTime": 140.7999969482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "これだけ撮れ高くれてやったんだから",
      "startTime": 143.2333304007,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kan007.wav",
      "text": "ちゃんと新曲の宣伝しないと、許さないから",
      "startTime": 145.7999969482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kor005.wav",
      "text": "まったくよね",
      "startTime": 149.4999970674,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そもそも、貴方のせいで取材を受ける羽目になったのよ",
      "startTime": 151.4000102917,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-mhk010.wav",
      "text": "一緒になって、したり顔で頷いていないでちょうだい",
      "startTime": 156.2000101725,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kor006.wav",
      "text": "もう散々文句聞いたわよ、そろそろいいでしょ！？",
      "startTime": 159.333343625,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "（なんか……曲を作ってる時より息が合ってるな）",
      "startTime": 163.933343625,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-koh004.wav",
      "text": "（結局、三人を団結させる『敵』は俺だった訳か……はぁ）",
      "startTime": 169.3666768391,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――二週間後　ライブバトル",
